# steane_logical_s — 논리 S = S†^⊗7 (transversal S†가 논리 S 구현). Tier-2 CLIFFORD(정준 stabilizer tableau, dense 미사용). plan=Clifford 게이트, no MatrixGate. 논리-정확성 witness=qec_logical 드라이버.
```python id=bloq
from qualtran import BloqBuilder
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import Hadamard, CNOT, ZPowGate
bb = BloqBuilder()
qs = [bb.add_register(f'q{i}', 1) for i in range(7)]
qs[0] = bb.add(ZPowGate(exponent=-0.5), q=qs[0])
qs[1] = bb.add(ZPowGate(exponent=-0.5), q=qs[1])
qs[2] = bb.add(ZPowGate(exponent=-0.5), q=qs[2])
qs[3] = bb.add(ZPowGate(exponent=-0.5), q=qs[3])
qs[4] = bb.add(ZPowGate(exponent=-0.5), q=qs[4])
qs[5] = bb.add(ZPowGate(exponent=-0.5), q=qs[5])
qs[6] = bb.add(ZPowGate(exponent=-0.5), q=qs[6])
bloq = bb.finalize(**{f'q{i}': qs[i] for i in range(7)})
```
